node.text:
I’m NOT saying burn yourself out and hustle every minute…

But what I am saying is that you can always find the time to work on your goals.

For example:

Instead of watching silly YouTube videos…

Instead of binging netflix…

Instead of overthinking…

You can use the time to learn something new or work on a goal you had for years.

It’s not just about how much time you have…

It’s how you use the time you have.

My recommendation for you:

Calculate for yourself how much time you have each week.

I’m sure you’ll be surprised.

And when you are ready to invest your time to start a business or side hustle…

follow 👉 @bjkuniversity 
follow 👉 @bjkuniversity 
follow 👉 @bjkuniversity 

...and they’ll show you the ropes.

node.text:
Friendly reminder:

You are overthinking.

It’s good to think and reflect about your life, of course.

But overthinking literally means that you are thinking more than necessary.

And as a result, you get paralyzed.

Want to know how to stop?

Act.

Just do something.

Some kind of decision is better than no decision.

Need something to start with?

Act now and…

follow 👉 @bjkuniversity 
follow 👉 @bjkuniversity 
follow 👉 @bjkuniversity

node.text:
Tell me why 97% of people :

are unsuccessful
are unfulfilled
have no control over their time
Barely can afford to live
hate their jobs and lives

It's not even their fault.

We live in a world where your network is your net worth and kids learn not to talk to strangers, and "networking" during class makes you fail.

This makes no sense to me.

You spend years learning irrelevant knowledge, that 5 five second Google search could tell you…

But not how to make it in life?

But that's what you get for following the system: Social anxiety, stress and being unhappy.

Of course not everyone feels like this. 

The system is not made for entrepreneurs, so we won't be happy like that and gotta take life into our own hands and solve the problem together.

Who else will teach people like us to be happy if we don't learn from each other?

That's why, if you wanna be an entrepreneur, don't be a lone wolf.

Get help and...

follow 👉 @bjkuniversity 
follow 👉 @bjkuniversity
follow 👉 @bjkuniversity

They'll show you how to build a business that works for you !

node.text:
You are not a victim of your circumstances!

Maybe you weren't born rich and wealthy…

But that doesn’t mean you have to stay unfortunate all your life.

Maybe you admire successful sportsmen, billionaires, or public figures...

But you think you can never be like them.

Well here is a new perspective for you:

You can be anything you want if you work towards it.

Take me as an example…

I was a war refugee.

I could have sat around and complained about how unfair my life is.

But I didn’t do that.

Instead, I worked towards a life that I wanted.

Was it always easy? No it wasn’t. 

But it was well worth it...

I’m telling you this because you can do the same.

Want to get started today?

...and embark on your journey towards the 1%.

node.text:
4 simple rules for life.

Learning these 4 things and implementing them in my life changed everything.

Especially when I learned to think less and act faster.

The longer you think, the more chances you have to talk yourself out of something.

But stopping yourself from overthinking isn’t always easy…

What makes it easier, though, is having supportive people around you.

If you are among other people who also work towards their goals…

They remind you to act.

You are less alone with your thoughts and everything gets easier.
